{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"@interface","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"MLNPointCollection","kind":"identifier"},{"text":" : ","kind":"text"},{"text":"MLNShape","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNShape","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"]}]},{"mentions":["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/GeoJSON"],"kind":"mentions"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can add point collections to the map by adding them to an "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object. Configure the appearance of an "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource"},{"type":"text","text":"’s or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorTileSource"},{"type":"text","text":"’s point collections collectively using an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCircleStyleLayer"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCircleStyleLayer"},{"type":"text","text":" object. To access a point"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"collection’s attributes, use an "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollectionFeature"},{"type":"text","text":" object."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You cannot add an "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection"},{"type":"text","text":" object directly to a map view as an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation. However, you can create individual "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" objects"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"from the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"coordinates"},{"type":"text","text":" array and add those annotation objects to the map view"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"using the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/addAnnotations:"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A point collection is known as a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"MultiPoint"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geometry in GeoJSON. Do not confuse "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection"},{"type":"text","text":" with "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the abstract superclass of "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibr